==English==
===Etymology===
From a slogan used to advertise Weet-Bix in Australia.

===Verb===
'''to [[have]] [[had]] [[one's]] [[Weet-Bix]] [[today]]'''

#(''Australia'') To [[exhibit]] plenty of [[vitality]] or [[strength]] or other superior [[performance]].

